					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yeah I guess that's the only reason not to use them - but then the tilemap would take up 4 times less VRAM if 16x16 tiles were used, probably compensating it largely.
<br />Another good reason is if you're using a 8x8 or 8x16 font on the same BG as the game's graphics - but as long as you use a separate BG for text I fail to see any reason not to use 16x16 tile mode.
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">16 colours oughta be enough to anybody, but don't quote me on it!<br /></div>
